attribute_information.CW_AGE_JUL2025_YR: Age (in years) of cow at the start of the trial, calculated from start date of trial period minus cow birthdate
attribute_information.CW_GENO_ID: The genotype identification number of the cows
attribute_information.CW_PGDT: Date cow is Preg-Checked, and often the same date as the calf is weaned (YYYY-MM-DD)
attribute_information.CW_PGPREG: Pregnancy diagnosis of cow at preg-check (P=Pregnant;O=Open;.=missing data)
attribute_information.CW_PGWT_KG: Cow weight at preg check in kg, collected from raw weight files
attribute_information.CW_Pred_PGWT_KG: Cow predicted Pregnancy Weight in kg
attribute_information.CW_REMARKS: Will include general remarks about the cow before and after prebreed, ie. Treatments, notes regarding fostering, etc.
attribute_information.CW_TAG: Corresponds to the visual cow ID tag
attribute_information.CW_YR_LETTER: Letter that reflects the year animal was born in
attribute_information.RANCH: The ranch where the animal belong (Kinsella or Mattheis)
attribute_information.RFI_gEPD: Cow genomic estimated Expected Progeny Difference
